                <h1>Change Your WhatsApp Background: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change your WhatsApp background, open the app and go to Settings. Tap on Chats, then Wallpaper. You can choose either a solid color or select an image from your gallery. Adjust the wallpaper to fit your screen, then confirm your choice. Enjoy a personalized chat experience with your new background!</p>
